regional anti-mining alliance in Southern Mindanao), South Cotabato People&#8217;s Alliance for 
Nationalism and Democracy (SOCPAND) and <i>Samahan ng mga Magsasaka sa Timog 
Kutabato</i> - SAMATIKU (South Cotabato Farmers Association).  </p>

